    "The release of the RailFOD23 dataset provides a valuable resource for researchers and developers to evaluate and improve object detection techniques for foreign object detection on railroad transmission lines.",
    "With this dataset, researchers can compare and evaluate different object detection algorithms, driving advancements in this field.",
    "Dataset characteristics.",
    "Table 1 provides an overview of the key characteristics of the transmission line foreign body dataset.",
    "The dataset is divided into three sub-datasets, AIGC-based, PS-based, and AUG-based, which represent data generated by AIGC generation, PS software generation, and image enhancement methods, respectively."
